title: HOUR 3- Chris Haynes Aug 26, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Chris Haynes Aug 26, 2020
description:
Chris Haynes tells Dan that it would be hard for the NBA to issue out punishment for Morris stepping on Doncic's bad ankle. Chris says it is too hard to prove the intent, But Chris tells Dan that it is definitely a bad look for Morris.
